鐘後再檢舉多次,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilentmajorityhk%2F&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16RaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=c9e0c859\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n22:45 ,檢舉<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;港人揮手區&quot;</span>專頁,5分鐘後再檢舉多次,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PeopleOfHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPeopleOfHK%2F&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16RaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=4904b81f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PeopleOfHK/</a> <br />\n<br />\n大家用 whatspp ,IG ,snapchat...等分享比朋友又好,口講又好,有Facebook既,應該要幫手檢舉! 增加對家文宣成本,我地香港人唔會屈服同認輸,大家請盡量分享出去~每人分享比10至20個朋友,記得晚上10點開始Facebook 集體檢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">上面4個係基本盤<br />\n<br />\n下面亦有DLC支線任免費俾唔夠喉既手足繼續玩！(遲d都會為佢地輪流發起每晚檢舉嘉年華)</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥沒有一個是無辜的🔥<br />\n如果大家嘅憤怒仲未平息，請繼續順序重覆Facebook 檢舉步驟❗❗❗<br />\n<br />\n😡除暴安良大聯盟<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%99%A4%E6%9A%B4%E5%AE%89%E8%89%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-106159104055088/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-106159104055088%2F&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16RaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=68cfe175\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%99%A4%E6%9A%B4%E5%AE%89%E8%89%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-106159104055088/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n😡時聞香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HongKongGoodNews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHongKongGoodNews%2F&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16RaCH8